  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposal, by reason of the increase in scale and bulk, would have a significant and harmful impact on the amenities enjoyed by residents of neighbouring premises to the north. The proposed roof extension would result in a loss of outlook and an increased sense of enclosure for surrounding properties.&amp;nbsp; As such, the proposal is contrary to policy D3 of the London Plan (2021), policies LP1 and LP2 of the Hackney Local Plan (LP33) (2020), and the stipulations of the council&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;By reason of its incongruous roof design, and window arrangement, the proposed development would result in an obtrusive and incompatible form of development that would fail to respect the character and appearance of the subject property and surrounding area. The proposed development fails to comply with policies D3 and D4 of the London Plan (2021), policies LP1 and LP2 of the Hackney Local Plan (LP33) (2020), and the stipulations of the council&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/p&gt;"
